sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant C as 🌐 Client
  participant A as ⚡ FastAPI App Service
  participant K as 🔐 Azure Table Storage
  participant D as 🗄️ Databricks SQL
  participant U as 📊 Unity Catalog Gold

  C->>A: GET /tables or /export/table.csv with X-API-Key
  A->>A: Validate header and hash with API_KEY_PEPPER
  A->>K: Lookup hash in gemsApiKeys
  K-->>A: Key metadata owner revokedAt lastUsedAt
  A->>A: Check revoked status owner allowlist and table allowlist
  A->>D: SELECT or DESCRIBE HISTORY using server PAT
  D->>U: Read gems_catalog.gold_v1 table
  U-->>D: Rows or Delta version metadata
  D-->>A: Query result
  A-->>C: JSON metadata or CSV stream
